ith US GAAP and IFRS&lt;br&gt;● Own the regulatory reporting calendar, ensuring all filings with the NFA, CFTC, and other&amp;nbsp;governing bodies are accurate and submitted on time&lt;br&gt;● Stay current on regulatory developments and proactively assess the impact on our&amp;nbsp;reporting and accounting processes&lt;br&gt;● Support external audits and assist

