&lt;li&gt;Draft, review, and negotiate a wide variety of commercial agreements, including:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Content and technology license agreements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Data licensing, access and sharing agreements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Software, SaaS, cloud services, platform, and technology services agreements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Other strategic commercial partnerships, vendor agreements, professional services agreements, and procurement-related contracts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide strategic and practical legal advice to business teams on contract structure, negotiation strategy, and risk management.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the continuous improvement of contract templates, negotiation playbooks, and workflows to promote efficiency and consistency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in managing outside counsel and coordinating specialized legal support as needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the wider company in building a leading digital gaming platform.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
