&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABOUT THE ROLE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re hiring a Creative Associate to own the look, feel, and creative quality of Fanatics Casino&#39;s organic social channels. This is a hands-on creative role — you&#39;ll be shooting, editing, designing, and creating content yourself, as well as overseeing what comes in from our agencies, UGC creators, and freelance partners. You&#39;ll work alongside the Social Media Manager and report to the Director of Social Media.&lt;/p&gt;
